  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel your <strong>potatoes</strong> and chop them into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Top, tail, peel and chop your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> roughly</p><p>Top, tail, peel and chop your<strong> parsnip[s]</strong> into quarters lengthways, then into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-10-1691497243621-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-10-1691497243621-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-10-1691497243621-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-10-1691497243621-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-10-1691497243621-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong>, <strong>chopped carrot</strong> and <strong>chopped parsnip</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 12-15 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once done, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-11-1691497248326-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-11-1691497248326-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-11-1691497248326-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-11-1691497248326-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-11-1691497248326-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>sausages</strong> to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until the sausages are cooked through</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-11-1691497251532-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-11-1691497251532-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-11-1691497251532-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-11-1691497251532-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-11-1691497251532-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>apple[s]</strong> finely (skin on), discarding the core</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>sliced apple</strong> with 1 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 1/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until starting to caramelise</p><p>Tip: Watch these like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-10-1691497255155-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-10-1691497255155-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-10-1691497255155-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-10-1691497255155-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-10-1691497255155-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the apple caramelises, dissolve your <strong>beef stock mix</strong>, <strong>onion marmalade</strong> and <strong>dried sage</strong> in 300ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [375ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[550ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>onion stock</strong></p><p>Once caramelised, add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>flour</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up until a sandy paste forms</p><p>Gradually stir in your <strong>onion stock</strong> and cook for 5 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains – this is your <strong>toffee apple gravy</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-9-1691497259971-x200.jpg",
