    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then add your <strong>green beans</strong> to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-9-1691497263245-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
